media:group.media:title: AI Wrote This Comedy Sketch
media:group.media:description:
Door Monster's Tiny Table Podcast - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xvOdR3UfZUo
Behind the Scenes - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=r-DvYsUH7HI

We thought it would be fun to try and generate an entire Door Monster script with an AI script generator, but of course our comedy instincts took over and we had to start responding to it - the first "video-within-a-video" part is an AI script, and then we the humans took over writing the human lines, but continued generating them for CopyKyle. 

Cool video about AI images from Corridor - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=W4Mcuh38wyM
